commentText: Get the HL7 acknowledgement payload associated with this exception, if any.__@return If the timeout occurred while attempting to receive an HL7 Message, this will be null.  If the timeout_occurred while attempting to receive an HL7 Acknowledgement, this will be the HL7 Message.  If the timeout occurred_while attempting to complete the read of an HL7 message (i.e. part of the message has already been read), this_will be the partial acknowledgement payload that was read before the timeout.
